Understaffed.

02:22.300 --> 02:28.700
Now, understaffed means that they don't have enough people working there.

02:28.700 --> 02:30.600
They don't have enough workers.

02:30.600 --> 02:32.800
Right, they don't have enough employees.

02:32.800 --> 02:33.600
Perfect.

02:33.600 --> 02:38.300
Okay, the next one is timing is just not right.

02:38.300 --> 02:40.900
The timing is just not right.

02:40.900 --> 02:43.900
The timing is just not right.

02:43.900 --> 02:46.500
The timing is just not right.

