03:34.800 --> 03:36.700
Wait off my shoulders.

03:36.700 --> 03:38.900
Wait off my shoulders.

03:38.900 --> 03:41.100
Wait off my shoulders.

03:41.100 --> 03:44.400
So, to take weight of my shoulders

03:44.400 --> 03:47.800
