03:50.600 --> 03:54.500
If you have a lot of things to do and I come and help you,

03:54.500 --> 03:57.700
that means that I took some of the weight off your shoulders.

03:57.700 --> 03:58.400
Yes.

03:58.400 --> 04:01.500
Let's look at the next phrase that we have here

04:01.500 --> 04:03.100
