04:39.700 --> 04:46.700
Here, let me give you a hand with your suitcase.

04:52.100 --> 04:52.900
All right.

04:52.900 --> 04:55.900
Give me a hand is another way of saying

04:55.900 --> 04:58.100
help or to help out.

04:58.100 --> 04:59.100
Exactly.

04:59.100 --> 05:00.100
To help out.

05:00.100 --> 05:01.100
Perfect.

05:01.100 --> 05:04.100
Now, the last phrase we're going to look at here

05:04.100 --> 05:07.700
