05:07.800 --> 05:09.600
Keep our costs down.

05:09.600 --> 05:12.100
Keep our costs down.

05:12.100 --> 05:14.800
Keep our costs down.

05:14.800 --> 05:21.300
So, to keep our costs down means to try and not spend so much money.

05:21.300 --> 05:22.100
Exactly.

05:22.100 --> 05:27.600
Many companies, for example, now control how much printing you do.

05:27.600 --> 05:28.600
Yes.

05:28.600 --> 05:30.600
Right, to keep the cost down of paper.

05:30.600 --> 05:36.600
Yes, so in other words, they do not want to have unnecessary spending.

05:36.600 --> 05:37.600
Perfect.

